  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Scramble into the cockpit of the only combat jet fighter game on Game Boy! The Navy F-14 Tomcat, a hero of the Persian Gulf War, soars to new heights in this first-person aerial assault simulator.\n* Fully instrumented control panels!\n* HUD for enemy targeting; radar and landing displays for smooth navigation!\n* Complete 360 rotation!\n* Wing-mounted 50mm cannons; AIM-54 air-to-air missiles; ECM system to confuse oncoming warheads!\n* Dynamic aircraft carrier takeoff and landing; in-flight refueling!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
